Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Select
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,惡已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都準備好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始排除惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,負熊能量開始充填
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗶哩嗶哩 下作下～作
