Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在法庭上得到他們的百合承認
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,熊就能變成女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要想得到百合承認就必須捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自己最珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這只是露露的猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那時的銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是把從紅紅那裡得到的愛意捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為了實現願望而捨棄愛意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,百合裁判就此開庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,被告人 椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你有要申述的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想永遠和銀子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,請將銀子變成人類的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,裁判長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,被告犯下了傲慢之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有罪 Guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢就是想要改變百合城銀子身份的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因為熊是會被排除的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且銀子她成為人之後一定會更幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇 真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,鋥鋥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才說你的想法是傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是傲慢也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請將銀子變成人類的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不過有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須捨棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,簡而言之 你會忘記銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,夢醒時分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會拒絕她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拒絕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我許下了不能許下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,誤以為自己那一廂情願的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,便是世間真理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那一刻終會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,透明風暴咆哮而至之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你將會找到百合城銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若你和她再次成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,成功交換誓約之吻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就能永遠在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,鋥鋥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼被告人 椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你要讓百合城銀子成為人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抑或 你要放棄愛意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會放棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請將銀子變成人類的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我以最珍貴的東西為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,許下了想讓銀子成為人類的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,百合裁判就此開庭
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被告人 椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你承認自己的罪行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經犯下了傲慢之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,許下了想讓銀子成為人類女孩子的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 在透明風暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到自己的所求了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.32,Text1,,0,0,150,,{\fad(450,0)}回 憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,教給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的所求——真愛找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,純花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不忘記愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就永遠不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不放棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,即使失去了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也不會變得透明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要縱身墜入風暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這… 這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,露露 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把這顆星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把真正的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,交給銀子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷嗚嗷嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是食人熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,獨孤求愛的銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來吃你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快點開槍打死我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就要把大家全吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是罪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷嗚嗷嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,紅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,終於 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,熊利亞大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 熊利亞大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要恢復原貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我們也該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是Sexy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇啵嗒～嘟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,鋥鋥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.04,Text1,,38,0,203,,{\fad(350,0)}熊利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.04,Text2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)}{\pos(1119,1009.5)\fsp0\fscx110}愛之星
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,椿輝紅羽
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的愛意 是真心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:14:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是真心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,…打碎我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,熊利亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,請您將我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,變成熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,百合 承認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這… 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,紅羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,銀子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你始終不忘記愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你始終不放棄愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我給你… 誓約之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們從今以後永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷嗚嗷嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,百合 承認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,超… 超不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人竟然變成了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼…可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們 已經不能開炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你… 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那已經不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,惡必須排除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,別思考
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在我們的齊心協力之下終於做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我們成功地排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,蔓延在這所學園裡的可怕的惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來我們還是必須成為透明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 讓我們開始排除儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友 是重於一切的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻在這裡的朋友 就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.71,Text1,,0,0,150,,回 憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,無法融入我們的人是在給我們添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這種不合群的人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 讓我們決定下一個需要排除的惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:08.62,Text2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1432,814)\frz39}故\N障
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了
